        <item>
          <title>VW Group Models Affected in Data Breach, 800,000 Vehicles Exposed</title>
          <description><![CDATA[A data breach affecting over 800,000 VW Group models has been reported, with more than half sharing precise GPS location data. The vulnerability was discovered by a European hacking organization and acknowledged by Cariad, a subsidiary of Volkswagen's automotive software." maxlengt="160]]></description>
